1
00:00:03,400 --> 00:00:06,200
This course works differently than what you're probably used to.

2
00:00:06,710 --> 00:00:07,850
 Here's what to expect.

3
00:00:08,360 --> 00:00:11,270
 You'll work on a real project for a real organization, as part of a 

4
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:11,620
team.

5
00:00:12,170 --> 00:00:15,090
 The people you're delivering to aren't grading you on a rubric.

6
00:00:15,690 --> 00:00:17,680
 They have an actual need for what you produce.

7
00:00:18,910 --> 00:00:23,480
 That changes the stakes. There are no exams. No final papers.

8
00:00:23,810 --> 00:00:26,630
 You're assessed on the work you create, the professional skills you 

9
00:00:26,690 --> 00:00:29,630
demonstrate, and your ability to reflect on your own growth.

10
00:00:30,145 --> 00:00:32,805
 The artifacts you produce and the thinking behind them are what 

11
00:00:32,855 --> 00:00:36,175
matter. AI is part of the process here.

12
00:00:36,475 --> 00:00:40,322
 You'll learn how to use it as a professional tool. More on that soon.

13
00:00:41,132 --> 00:00:43,782
 You won't get all the content up front and apply it at the end.

14
00:00:44,452 --> 00:00:47,702
 Instead, you'll pick up new skills and frameworks along the way, 

15
00:00:48,392 --> 00:00:50,502
right when you need them for the work you're doing that week.

16
00:00:51,842 --> 00:00:54,582
 And there are regular checkpoints built in throughout the course to

17
00:00:54,632 --> 00:00:55,602
 help you stay on track.

18
00:00:56,252 --> 00:00:58,482
 You're not on your own until the final deadline.

19
00:00:58,992 --> 00:01:00,822
 It might feel unfamiliar at first.

20
00:01:01,522 --> 00:01:04,412
 There's no single right answer, and your team is counting on you to

21
00:01:04,472 --> 00:01:05,622
 show up and contribute.

22
00:01:06,492 --> 00:01:08,782
 That's what professional work actually looks like.

23
00:01:09,232 --> 00:01:12,012
 Learning to navigate it is one of the most valuable things you'll take

24
00:01:12,052 --> 00:01:12,852
 from this course.